湮灭過程遵守[[爱因斯坦|爱因斯坦]]的[[质能关系式|质能关系式]]E=mc<sup>2</sup>以及[[動量守恆|動量守恆]]。<ref name=Particleadventure.org>
{{cite web
 |title=The Standard Model – Particle decays and annihilations
